high_descs: Turn your back and walk into the room ahead, then turn right to walk toward a cabinet; face the cabinet.
Open the closet and retrieve the knife; close the knife when done.
Exit the room, go to the back of sofa at the far corner of living room, where there is a pot on the sofa.
Put the knife on the pot.
Pick up the stack of pot and knife.
Turn around and walk toward the round coffeetable on the left nearby.
Put the pot with a knife on it over the far end of the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife on the fry pan over the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around to exit the room and reach the cabinet on the right.
Pick up the knife from the cupboard.
Turn right to head out of the bedroom and turn right to reach the back of the pot.
Put the knife on the pot.
Pick up the pot from the couch.
Turn left to reach the coffeetable.
Put the pot on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife on the round table.

high_descs: Turn two left to go into the bedroom to the cabinet.
Pick up the yellow handled knife in the armoire.
Leave the room take a right and go behind the left couch to the pot on the couch.
Place the knife in the blue pot.
Pick up the pot with a knife in it.
Turn around and go to the coffeetable behind you.
Place the pot on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the Pot with a Knife in it on the CoffeeTable.
